/home/fanyx/mine/FeMPC/example/biometric/main.go
func mpcmain(db [][]int32, sample []int32) int32 {
	min := distance(db[0][0], db[0][1], sample[0], sample[1])
	for i := 0; i < N; i++ {
		dist := distance(db[i][0], db[i][1], sample[0], sample[1])
		if dist < min {
			min = dist
		}
	}
	return min
}
